::Hot Rod::

"Rodimus Prime, is me.," he says, to Feline.
"In the year 2005, I was at Autobot city, on Earth. The Decepticons
attacked, and Megatron killed Optimus Prime." He left out, that he was
partially responsible, for that.
"The Matrix, and command, was given to Ultra Magnus. The Matrix was then
stolen by Galvatron, who was Megatron, rebuilt by Unicron. Fighting
Unicron, to save Cybertron, I fought Galvatron, inside Unicron. I got
the Matrix, and used its power, to destroy Unicron. Its power and
knowlage also changed me into Rodimus Prime. I lead the Autobots, untill
2007. I then gave command back to a revived Optimus, after the hate
plague crisis."

OOC: Feline has one of the most famous "good guys" in her hands.

::DrillBit::

He got out of the CR, and found KitKat.
"Whats going on?"
